{"tid":1525759,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開) 建議增強黑警資料庫功能","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:17:16.000Z","uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1359a3a975d421be4578188057c4a95dfa0b99","tid":1525759,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"呢個post主要分3部份<br />\n1. 總結一下資料庫作用<br />\n2. 如何增強資料庫<br />\n3. 其他建議<br />\n<br />\n<ins>1.資料庫作用</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 香港人金魚記億 <br />\n無文字記下罪行 <br />\n就會很快唔記得咩事  <br />\n<br />\n2. 系統化記下各類暴行，罪行 <br />\n方便將來紐倫堡式大審判<br />\n<br />\n3. 方便西方世界知道呢班人搞咩<br />\n<br />\n以第三項為例<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美關員查手機  見反美網帖拒入境</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都唔知聽日會發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n可能佢地十年後搞移民<br />\n式者佢地個寶貝仔女 <br />\n去 外國 讀書，工作<br />\n<br />\n就係死係今日堆暴行上<br />\n就好像3個月前都無人估到反送中 <br />\n會搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2. 如何增強資料庫</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 增加英文解說  令全世界知發生咩事<br />\n2. 增強介面 例如search engine<br />\n3. 包括包括黑警以外 其他種類人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>先講第2項</strong><br />\n例如可以  用警區/階級/部門來做filter<br />\n<br />\n以PPRB 果3條友為例<br />\n佢地比較繁密出來講野<br />\n市民對佢地印象極強 <br />\n<br />\n可以直接search PPRB<br />\n查到呢幾條友的堆指黑為白說法<br />\n謝振中的疑似性問題資料<br />\n<br />\n又好像鄧炳強作為元朗警察指揮官年代的白粉當鹽案<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563877346039&amp;issue=20190723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563877346039%26issue%3D20190723&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=b1c1872c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563877346039%26issue%3D20190723&h=58b1d2f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563877346039&amp;issue=20190723</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>再講第3樣</strong> <br />\n都幾多人 未包括在黑警資料庫入面<br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGZwE3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGZwE3N.jpg&h=18e4b631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罪行<br />\n<br />\n物化示威者 <br />\n製造一個令政府可以進行大屠殺<br />\n的社會氣氛<br />\n<br />\n由一隻曱甴到一百萬人屠殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%80%E9%9A%BB%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%259A%25BB%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%25AE%25BA%2F&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=b1bda8d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%259A%25BB%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%25AE%25BA%2F&h=4bb2d971\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B1%E4%B8%80%E9%9A%BB%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n為何罵人為「曱甴」會使你失去人性- The News Lens 關鍵評論網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://hk.thenewslens.com/amparticle/123475&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj-6_rMvK7kAhXSPXAKHRx9BZAQFjABegQIBRAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw3EyK-ycGw_6RhKLf4Le9yC&amp;ampcf=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F123475%26ved%3D2ahUKEwj-6_rMvK7kAhXSPXAKHRx9BZAQFjABegQIBRAB%26usg%3DAOvVaw3EyK-ycGw_6RhKLf4Le9yC%26ampcf%3D1&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=4826aca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://hk.thenewslens.com/amparticle/123475&amp;ved=2ahUKEwj-6_rMvK7kAhXSPXAKHRx9BZAQFjABegQIBRAB&amp;usg=AOvVaw3EyK-ycGw_6RhKLf4Le9yC&amp;ampcf=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又例如  國泰</span><br />\n(犯罪者 新CEO)<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0889rLs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0889rLs.png&h=7748c096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罪行  <br />\n<br />\n解僱大量政見不同人士<br />\n (藍絲0 黃絲 幾十  炒果班未見過有藍絲)<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵告密，篤灰文化<br />\n建立秘密警察制度<br />\n打壓民主，自由<br />\n(班鬼佬會考慮呢樣野 <br />\n國泰本身都唔係特別平)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又好像最新港鐵</span><br />\n(犯罪者：全體高層)<br />\n<br />\n罪行  <br />\n多次疑似協助 <br />\n政府，黑社會 <br />\n發動大規模針對平民的攻擊事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721，811，831<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3.其他建議</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 如果工程量太大 (例譯英文)<br />\n可以考慮眾籌/尋找協助<br />\n<br />\n2,保安上要做得比較好<br />\n要定期 backup<br />\n因為長遠會令到一堆共狗想hack<br />\n/搞死個網  好像連登呢2日的ddos<br />\n<br />\n3.最好係海外巴絲搞<br />\n(起碼最後經手人)<br />\n要知道 香港依家真係唔安全"},{"pid":"3b7103b68d413e006a4756efbd091f4f7c64b540","tid":1525759,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"817